    <blockquote>
      <p>
        <span>Welcome to the heart of </span><a href="/table-of-contents"
          >A Severed Story</a
        ><span
          >. The chapters before this one introduced you to Lumon, and future
          chapters will help you build your employee. <strong
            >Here, we explain how the game is actually played</strong
          > — the actions an employee may attempt, the consequences they invite, and
          the qualities of your character that tip the odds toward success.</span>
      </p>
    </blockquote>
    <div data-panel-type="warning">
